      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, this picture that I'm facing and you are facing here, it is me in a full officer's dress uniform.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this picture was taken back my hometown in Leduc, where my family was living at the time when I returned from the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
